            <p class="lead">Most new hosts spend money in the wrong places. They buy expensive art and decorative pillows, then cut corners on the mattress. <strong>This guide is built around ROI: what actually drives 5-star reviews, higher nightly rates, and repeat bookings for Toronto Airbnb hosts.</strong> The median Toronto 2-bedroom earns $2,337 per month. Top performers hit $5,414. Furnishing is one of the few controllable variables that separates the two.</p>
