          <h2 id="investment-spectrum">The Furnishing Investment Spectrum</h2>
          <p>There is no single right budget for furnishing an Airbnb. The right number depends on your property, your market position, and what's already in the unit. Here's how the three tiers break down.</p>

          <div class="table-container">
            <table class="rules-table">
