              <span class="alt-number">8</span>
              <h4>Professional Photos: $200&ndash;$400</h4>
              <p>This isn't a furnishing item, but it belongs on this list. Professional photography is the highest-ROI marketing spend available to an Airbnb host. It makes a $5,000 furnishing setup look like a $10,000 one. Airbnb's own data shows professionally photographed listings earn significantly more. Don't skip it.</p>
