              <h4>Bathroom Second</h4>
              <p>Hotel-white towels (two per guest), a quality bath mat, a clear mirror with good lighting, and a supply caddy stocked with full-size toiletries. Bathrooms are photographed, noticed, and judged closely. A clean, well-stocked bathroom is a 5-star signal.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

